sive VR Experience:\n        Fully immerse yourself in a beautifully crafted, gigantic space with state-of-the-art VR graphics. Feel the tension as you navigate through vast rooms filled with high-tech gadgets and traps.\n\n    Stealth and Strategy:\n        Use your cunning and skills to outsmart the colossal room owner. Plan your heist meticulously, use shadows to your advantage, and deploy advanced tools to avoid detection.", "short_description": "Description:\nStep into the shoes of a master thief in the thrilling VR game \"Thief in the Colossus.\" Your mission is to \"borrow\" precious items from an enormous, high-tech space, while avoiding detection by the colossal room owner. This immersive game offers an unparalleled blend of stealth, strategy, and futuristic adventure, set in a sprawling, technologically advanced environment."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/thief-in-the-colossus/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Jame Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/thief-in-the-colossus", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7612113488916145"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1626491858173038"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id":